OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and widely sunny day
OL,6,Ftoday across the region, with perhaps
OL,7,Fsome cloud bubbling up later in the
OL,8,Fday. Another hot day with temperatures
OL,9,Fway above average for the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine and warm evening for
OL,12,Fmany, although the odd thunderstorm
OL,13,Fmay develop across the south.
OL,14,FRemaining warm overnight with perhaps
OL,15,Fsome cloud moving into eastern areas.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,18,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Not as hot as
OL,19,Frecent days but still feeling very
OL,20,Fwarm, especially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
