OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry and settled,
OL,7,Falthough a few showers may develop
OL,8,Ffrom time to time. Very warm initially
OL,9,Fbut it will begin to cool a little by
OL,10,Fthe weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
